{"tid":1691371,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣］試下將黑警同甴近平拉埋一齊講？","createTime":"2019-11-03T15:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T10:15:16.000Z","uid":71887,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3de5815957d627916e508245e212d4f7c5895a76","tid":1691371,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"見到有個po係講 將黑警同解放軍拉埋一齊抬高黑警貶低解放軍 令國內小粉紅產生矛盾 <br />\n<br />\n係微博撐警 表掦香港警察 再踩低公安解放軍 !!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1689332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1689332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我發現點解中國嘅人同班藍屍會咁支持黑警所為 係因為佢哋相信班狗所做嘅 真係維持緊社會秩序 係愛國嘅表現 <br />\n<br />\n我覺得雖然依家好多文宣都有講警權過大 但藍絲/所謂愛國既大陸人一定會支持班狗既做法 而文宣係做比對家睇 唯一打破佢地支持既方向 只可以從「愛國」哩個point入手 班狗連國家都唔放在眼內 分化班藍絲同小粉紅再去支持班人渣 如果支持班狗就係唔放甴近平在眼內！<br />\n<br />\n 加上 依家大陸啲人都係用一種隔岸觀火既態度睇香港 不論中共定平民都係 無論班狗點濫權都唔關佢地事 要搞都係林奠處理 但着眼妹仔大過主人婆 一燒到國家佢地就一定唔接受<br />\n<br />\n我覺得文宣應該著重講軍權過大 一個軍政府係連阿爺都唔會放在眼內 歷代嘅中國君王 最忌嘅係功高蓋主 妹仔大過主人婆係中國黎講真係諗都唔好諗 建議文宣可以整一份 （意思係）黑警用腳踩住維尼同林奠 手握人民性命嘅文宣圖 大肆宣揚呢張文宣 不斷煲大黑警連甴近平都唔放在眼內既事<br />\n<br />\n小女不才 畫圖唔叻 唯有上連登請文宣組幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家討論下哩個方向可唔可行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwBPMya.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwBPMya.jpg&h=a25ef2eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8m9eddH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8m9eddH.jpg&h=0f16cf6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XLXVr3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XLXVr3.jpg&h=a6e77ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzXLjTK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzXLjTK.jpg&h=27e16705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33VpAr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33VpAr5.jpg&h=77de239d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4EObfr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4EObfr6.jpg&h=4c279f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1tzqjTN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1tzqjTN.jpg&h=3d97b7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D7Eav0t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD7Eav0t.jpg&h=b347043a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7o26yP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7o26yP.jpg&h=0773f714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZUYETQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZUYETQ.jpg&h=e58eb7b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f34a3b2d3c95f6648916a258fe6608f72d50a71","tid":1691371,"uid":297569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家嚟睇下 時刻保持冷靜同分析能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8907fac92a38a0162a935a65d8566fceb39c6b4d","tid":1691371,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d1919ba6ddaf759eac57bcdbb1ddbcdb9991ad4a","tid":1691371,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"甴近平！！"},{"pid":"f4ede4c918e219e86a7f827645b176d541593004","tid":1691371,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"49a93a8cb18c7e89874a530de02bd47860ea0602","tid":1691371,"uid":71887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"2740e37a24e61c25a25a4b291d802eb23f1d941c","tid":1691371,"uid":39174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"